{
  "stem": "20848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't even remember very much what he did during the day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He certainly didn't work, because there was no work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were refugees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- I don't remember what he did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know that later on my mother went back to Lodz on a train with my cousin who lived in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my cousin didn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they brought materials back from our shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow or other, they smuggled a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we lived from that, because we were selling this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And later on, one day, I remember there was a blackmailer came into our house-- a Pole.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I really have to admire my father's courage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He came to this flat, and he said that if my father won't pay him a certain amount of money, he's going to go the SS and tells him that we are selling materials and things like that, that we're smuggling materials.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father took him at the lapel and said to him, you clear out of my house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If you want to go to Germans, you go right ahead and go to Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know where he got his-- he was a very courageous man, my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I never-- never heard from him again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course we didn't go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't run to Russia because it was a terribly, terribly cold winter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was such a cold winter that when my mother sent me for milk across the road in a saucepan, the milk was suddenly frozen by the time I brought it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine how cold it was?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And because I was still very young and my brother was even younger, my parents were scared to run to Russia in this cold weather.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
